telling people that, would I?

215
00:12:07,566 --> 00:12:10,200
Duncan, I thought you and Peter
should hang out this summer.

216
00:12:10,202 --> 00:12:12,803
<i>Lord knows he brought enough
of his Star Wars dolls.</i>

217
